  "prompt": "What are the Yojana in Chhattisgarh?",
  "response": "Chhattisgarh government has implemented several Yojanas (welfare schemes) across various sectors. Some prominent Yojanas include:\n\n1. Agriculture and Rural Development Yojanas:\n- Rajiv Gandhi Kisan Nyay Yojana\n- Godhan Nyay Yojana\n- Narva, Garva, Ghurva, Badi Yojana\n\n2. Women Empowerment Yojanas:\n- Mukhyamantri Mahila Samman Kendra Yojana\n- Pradhan Mantri Matru Vandana Yojana\n\n3. Health Yojanas:\n- Mukhyamantri Swasthya Bima Yojana\n- Rashtriya Swasthya Bima Yojana\n\n4. Education Yojanas:\n- Mukhyamantri Vidyarthi Suraksha Yojana\n- Mukhyamantri Kanya Vivah Yojana\n\n5. Employment Yojanas:\n- Mukhyamantri Rojgar Yojana\n- Mahatma Gandhi National Rural Employment Guarantee Scheme\n\nThese Yojanas aim to provide social welfare, economic support, and development opportunities to the people of Chhattisgarh.",
